                Mr. Mander
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2eed18a0-7850-4756-a675-7f196926ee5c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
